```

## Template Building Blocks — REQUIRED

Every template MUST include these pages/sections:

| Page | Purpose | Required Content |
|------|---------|------------------|
| **Portfolio** | Landing/Home | Photo gallery, name, brief intro |
| **About** | Personal story | Bio, measurements, hair/eye color, agency |
| **Services** | Business info | Rates, comp card, booking types |
| **Contact** | Lead generation | Contact form, social links, location |

